org.xbib.elasticsearch.index.analysis.skos.engine.jena
Class SKOSEngineImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.xbib.elasticsearch.index.analysis.skos.engine.jena.SKOSEngineImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SKOSEngine
public class SKOSEngineImpl
extends Object
implements SKOSEngine

A Lucene-backed SKOSEngine Implementation. Each SKOS concept is stored/indexed as a Lucene document. All labels are converted to lowercase
